    a skos:Concept ;
    dcterms:source "Bignall J, McCallum K, O’Neill S, Laws M, Potter T, Morgan R, Cox B, Sparrow B (2023) Invertebrate Fauna Module. In ‘Ecological Field Monitoring Protocols Manual using the Ecological Monitoring System Australia’. (Eds S O’Neill, K Irvine, A Tokmakoff, B Sparrow). TERN, Adelaide." ;
